  ∂(b,c,d)-∂(c,d,a) = (c,d)-(b,d)+(b,c) - (d,a)+(c,a)-(c,d)
                      = -(b,d)+(b,c)-(d,a)+(c,a)
                      = C₁-C₂. ✓

Case 2: d→c.
  {b,d,c}: b→d (from C₂), d→c, b→c (from C₁). TRANSITIVE.
  {a,d,c}: d→c, c→a (from C₁), d→a (from C₂). TRANSITIVE.
